    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Flirt</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Don't make me say it explicitly </l>
          <l>Don't make me define </l>
          <l>Don't make me put it into words </l>
          <l>I cannot seem to find </l>
          <l>Look into my eyes </l>
          <l>the first thing comes to mind </l>
          <l>Won't be a lie </l>
          <l>Some Originality a touch of honesty </l>
          <l>Won't do you harm </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>You seem so nice </l>
          <l>I would love to have one minute with you </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Don't ask me questions predictably </l>
          <l>Please don't be so dry </l>
          <l>Don't stare at me unmanly </l>
          <l>It don't make you look too fly </l>
          <l>Some Originality a touch of honesty </l>
          <l>Won't do you harm </l>
          <l>There's no need to be so deep </l>
          <l>It's only just one flirt </l>
          <l>And then goodbye</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
